\ip \bd ?N…ômeg…ôh…ôn tahro nulan nian t…ôm…ôte?\bd* Pol tat…ôn m…ôm…ô in tolkeike m…ôm…ô otuw…®n mehm i…ôfak m…®n …ôp…ôh Rom, uaris…®g in t…ôpanuw…®n e kantri u Spen. M…ôto aup…ôn ik…®n, in ot…ôk…ôike muw…®n mos m…ôni neen o nos-ip…ôn…ôn k…ôm ian-rat m…®n e nim…ôfak r…ôha Jerusalem. E nim…ôfak r…ôha Rom, Iaihlu…ô m…®n tep…ôt, m…ôto net…ôm Isrel tep…ôt m…®n.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte naoa u o naka?\bd* Uaris…®g Pol tatuw…®n Rom, in tolkeike m…ôm…ô ilat okotaup…ôn mot…®tun in, k…ôn in…ôh, in t…ôm…ôte naoa u. Net…ôm Rom k…ôsotos…ôn …ôh n…ôg…ôtun…ôn kit r…ôha aposol kit. K…ôn in…ôh, in tolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…ôn-iar…ôp suat…®p …ôtuat…®p r…ôha Uhg…®n o nosmeg…ôh…ôn net…ômim. K…ôn in tolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…ôn …ôsas m…ôm…ô otahro min nulan, Iaihlu…ô m…®n ne net…ôm Isrel, ilat rafin okotuwa kiti…ôh …ôm e nim…ôfak r…ôha Uhg…®n.  
\c 1  
\s1 Pol t…ôm…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm ilat  
\m
\v 1 Io Pol, u io slef kit r…ôha Kristo Iesu. Uhg…®n t…ômaun-in io m…ôm…ô io aposol, k…ôn t…ôm…®t…ôpun m…®l…ôs-ip…ôr io m…ôm…ô ek…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r r…ôhan.\x - \xo 1:1 \xt W…ôk 9:15 \x*\fig |alt="Roman street scene" src="HK00242B.TIF" size="span" loc="Rom 1:1" ref="Rom 1:1" \fig*  
\v 2 Namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r u, in t…®n…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s nuw…ôh r…ôk…®s e r…ôhan ien m…®n it…ôm k…ômot…ôte-p…ôn e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n.\x - \xo 1:2 \xt Rom 16:25-26 \x*  
\v 3-4 Namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r …ôh tat…ôghat-in N…ôt…®n, Iesu Kristo r…ôhatat I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô. In t…ômuwa et…ômim kit e noanol r…ôha Kig Tef…®t. K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô in N…ôt…®n …ôtuat…®p nian t…ômosmeg…ôh in e n…®m…®s…ôn e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn e w…ôk r…ôha Narm…®n asim.  
\v 5 E Kristo, Uhg…®n t…ômol t…ôw…®r k…ôm io, mos-ipa k…ôm io w…ôk w…®r m…ôm…ô io aposol kit. T…ômos-ipa w…ôk …ôh m…ôm…ô ekaun-in net…ômim e n…®ki Iaihlu…ô\f + \fr 1:5 \ft N…ôghat…ôn u ‚ÄúIaihlu…ô‚Äù tat…ôghat-in net…ômim rafin it…ôm s…ôn…ôm…ô noanol r…ôha Isrel.\f* m…®n e noanol m…®n rafin m…ôm…ô okot…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn lan, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan, moatol n…ôwian. K…ôn nian koatol n…ôhlan, ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…® Iesu.\x - \xo 1:5 \xt W…ôk 26:16-18; Kal 2:7-9 \x*  
\v 6 K…ôn it…ômat m…®n, Uhg…®n t…ômaun-in it…ômat m…ôm…ô it…ômat r…ôha Iesu Kristo.   
\p
\v 7 K…ôn roiu ek…ôte naoa k…ôm it…ômat rafin …ôp…ôh Rom it…ôm Uhg…®n tolkeike it…ômat, k…ôn t…ômaun-in it…ômat m…ôm…ô r…ôhan.  
\p P…ôs Uhg…®n Tata r…ôhatat, ne I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu Kristo okuawte-in r…ôhalau n…ôw…®r…ôn ne n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn k…ôm it…ômat.\x - \xo 1:7 \xt Nam 6:25-26 \x*   
\s1 Pol t…ômolkeike m…ôm…ô otuw…®n m…ôplan net…ôm Rom  
\p
\v 8 Uaris…®g epan…ôghat, iak…ôn tagkiu k…ôm r…ôhak Uhg…®n e Iesu Kristo ot…ômat rafin ag…®n-…ôh, m…ôto-inu net…ômim rafin e n…ôtueint…ôn k…ômot…ôto namnus…ôn e nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhat…ômat.  
\v 9 K…ôn Uhg…®n t…®tun m…ôm…ô e nian rafin iat…ôfak, k…ôn m…ôsaluin…ôn it…ômat. Iatol p…®k w…ôk r…ôhan e n…®kik rafin o n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r e N…ôt…®n.  
\v 10 K…ôn iat…ôfak m…ôm…ô ok…ôm…ô in n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn pahrien r…ôha Uhg…®n, in oter…ôh e suat…®p kit m…ôm…ô ek…®mn…ô m…ôplan it…ômat.\x - \xo 1:10 \xt W…ôk 19:21; Rom 15:23 \x*  
\v 11 Iakolkeike p…®k m…ôm…ô ek…®mn…ô m…ôplan it…ômat m…ôm…ô ekawte-in k…ôm it…ômat n…ôw…®r…ôn kit r…ôha Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô otol it…ômat nakot…ôtul …ôskas…®k t…ôhm…®n m…®n.  
\v 12 N…®p…ôt…® n…ôghat…ôn u m…ôm…ô, nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhat…ômat t…®tun nasitu…ôn lak, k…ôn r…ôhak m…®n t…®tun nasitu…ôn et…ômat.   
\p
\v 13 Piak m…®n ne w…®n…®k m…®n, t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô n…ôkot…®tun m…ôm…ô nian tep…ôt, r…ôhak n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôht m…ôm…ô ek…®mn…ô muag it…ômat. M…ôto nian rafin nat…®mnat neen koatahtos…®g-in io o n…®mn…ô…ôn. Iakolkeike m…ôm…ô r…ôhak w…ôk otoe-in noan e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat, tahmen e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha Iaihlu…ô m…®n ik…®n p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n.\x - \xo 1:13 \xt W…ôk 19:21 \x*  
\v 14 Ek…ôk…ôike m…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm net…ômim rafin it…ôm s…ôn…ôm…ô noanol r…ôha Isrel, net…ôm it…ôm kot…®tun n…ôghat…ôn Kris ne nol…ôn r…ôhalat, ne net…ôm it…ôm kot…ôruru, k…ôn ilat it…ôm k…ômotol-w…®r skul, ne ilat it…ôm k…ôsotol-w…®r…ôn skul. ∆èw…ôh, ek…ôk…ôike m…ôn-iar…ôp k…ôm ilat rafin.  
\v 15 K…ôn o nat …ôh, iakolkeike p…®k m…ôm…ô ek…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat m…®n …ôp…ôh Rom.   
\p
\v 16 Iat…ôghat min-n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu, io esaul…®s-in…ôn namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r. Esaul…®s…ôn m…ôto-inu namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r in n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n o nosmeg…ôh…ôn net…ômim rafin it…ôm koatahat…ôt…ô lan, t…ômaup…ôn muwa o noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel, uaris…®g u, o Iaihlu…ô m…®n.\x - \xo 1:16 \xt Mak 8:38; W…ôk 13:46; 1 Kor 1:18-24 \x*  
\v 17 Tol n…ôhlan, e namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r, Uhg…®n t…ômol …ôp suat…®p r…ôhan m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n tatos-ip…ôn r…ôhan …ôm n…ôtuat…®p…ôn k…ôm net…ômim. E nahat…ôt…ô…ôn …ôm, Uhg…®n tatol m…ôm…ô net…ômim kotuwa mot…ôtuat…®p e n…®gan…ômt…®n. K…ôn inu tahmen e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNet…ômim it…ôm kot…ôtuat…®p e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n e nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhalat, ilat okotos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:17 \xt Hab 2:4; Rom 3:21-22\x*   
\s1 Nem…ôha tatol Uhg…®n o t…ôfag…ô rat rafin  
\p
\v 18 M…ôto Uhg…®n e nego e neai tat…ôg…ôtun r…ôhan nem…ôha ne nalp…®n…ôn o net…ômim rafin it…ôm koat…ôht n…ôwian moatol t…ôfag…ô rat. Ilat koat…ôtlos…®g-in n…®pahrien…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n e nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhalat,  
\v 19 m…ôto-inu ilat kot…®tun n…ôplan …ôtuat…®p…ôn nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm net…ômim kot…®tun n…®tun…ôn Uhg…®n lan. Tol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu Uhg…®n at…®p t…ôm…ôg…ôtun …ôtuat…®p ilat lan.\x - \xo 1:19 \xt W…ôk 14:15-17; 17:24-28 \x*  
\v 20 Okol net…ômim k…ôsot…ôplan …ôtuat…®p…ôn Uhg…®n e n…®gan…ômt…®lat. M…ôto t…ôm…ôtuoun e nian in t…ômol neai, ne n…ôpt…ôn, ne nat…®mnat rafin, k…ôn net…ômim rafin kot…®tun n…ôplan…ôn e n…®gan…ômt…®lat, nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm in t…ômol, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan, kot…®tun n…ôplan…ôn r…ôhan n…ôsan…ôn…ôn it…ôm tatuw…®n …ôm nulan namnun t…®k…ô, ne n…®pahrien…ôn m…ôm…ô in Uhg…®n, k…ôn mot…®tun n…®tun…ôn m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n in t…ôhrol nulan. O nat …ôh, et…ômim kit t…®k…ô it…ôm t…®tun n…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô in t…ôruru m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ôhrol nulan.\x - \xo 1:20 \xt Job 12:7-9; Sam 19:1 \x*   
\p
\v 21 Tol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu, nat …ôpnap…®n ilat k…ômot…®tun Uhg…®n m…ôs…®n, m…ôto k…ômotap…ôs n…®siaii…ôn m…ôm…ô in Uhg…®n, k…ôn m…ôsot…ôn…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô n…®kilat tagien o nat…®mnat in t…ômol k…ôm ilat. M…ôto n…®kilat t…ômat…ôht nalp…ôkau…ôn alm…ôl m…®n m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n tahro nulan, k…ôn n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhalat t…ômuwa mapin…ôp, m…®not…ôruru suat…®p it…ôm Uhg…®n tolkeike m…ôm…ô okot…®tun.\x - \xo 1:21 \xt Efes 4:17-18 \x*  
\v 22 Nat …ôpnap…®n ilat koat…ôn m…ôm…ô ilat kotenat…®g, m…ôto ilat k…ômotuwa ialm…ôl m…®n,\x - \xo 1:22 \xt Jer 10:14; 1 Kor 1:20 \x*  
\v 23 k…ôn k…ômotap…ôs n…ôfak…ôn k…ôm Uhg…®n it…ôm r…ôhan nep…ôt…ôn t…ôhag-…ôhag, k…ôn ot…ôs…®m…®s…ôn t…ôtat…®g lil…®n, k…ôn m…®not…ôtuoun moat…ôfak k…ôm narm…® nat m…®n it…ôm tahmen e net…ômim u okot…®m…®s nian kit, o tahmen e m…ôn…®g m…®n, o nat meg…ôh m…®n koataliw…ôk o koat…ôkioah.\x - \xo 1:23 \xt Dut 4:15-19; Sam 106:20 \x*   
\p
\v 24 O nat u, Uhg…®n t…ômap…ôs ilat meg…ôhan-in ilat m…ôm…ô okot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn …ôm nol…ôn rat m…®n it…ôm n…®kilat tolkeike m…ôm…ô okotol e n…®p…ôt…®lat. Tol n…ôhlan, ilat k…ômotol nol…ôn m…®n e n…®p…ôt…®lat it…ôm tol …ôm naul…®s…ôn.  
\v 25 Ilat k…ômotap…ôs n…®pahrien…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n motask…ôl…®m neiueiu…ô…ôn, k…ôn moat…ôfak moatol w…ôk k…ôm neai, ne n…ôpt…ôn, ne nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômol, m…ôto k…ômotap…ôs n…ôfak…ôn k…ôm Uhg…®n. M…ôto p…ôs kitat kot…ônwiwi in nian rafin namnun t…®k…ô. ∆èw…ôh.   
\p
\v 26 O nol…ôn m…®n …ôh it…ôm net…ômim k…ômotol k…ôm Uhg…®n, t…ômap…ôs ilat, meg…ôhan-in ilat m…ôm…ô okot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn …ôm nol…ôn rat m…®n it…ôm n…®kilat tolkeike m…ôm…ô okotol e n…®p…ôt…®lat it…ôm tol naul…®s…ôn …ôm. Nat …ôpnap…®n n…®p…®tan m…®n, m…ôto ilat kotap…ôs n…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn r…ôhalat n…ôman, moatit at…®p ilat m…®n, k…ôn nat u in nat p…®s…®n e it…ôm u Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu.  
\v 27 K…ôn e nol…ôn ahmen-ahmen …ôm, n…ôman m…®n, ilat k…ômotap…ôs nit…ôn r…ôhalat n…®p…®tan m…®n, moatolkeike p…®k n…ôman p…®s…®n m…®n. Ilat koatit at…®p ilat m…®n it…ôm tol naul…®s…ôn. K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn nalp…®n…ôn k…ôm ilat o r…ôhalat nol…ôn rat ag…®n m…®n.\x - \xo 1:27 \xt Lev 18:22; 20:13; 1 Kor 6:9 \x*   
\p
\v 28 K…ôn nat kit m…®n. M…ôto-inu ilat k…ôsotolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô okot…®tun Uhg…®n, in t…ômap…ôs ilat meg…ôhan-in ilat m…ôm…ô r…ôhalat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôs…®tun…ôn m…ôm…ô nat kit in t…ôw…®r o nat kit in t…ôrat, k…ôn meg…ôhan-in m…ôm…ô okotol nat it…ôm t…ôs…ôtuat…®p…ôn m…ôm…ô okotol.  
\v 29 N…®kilat t…ôm…ôrioah e nol…ôn rat p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n rafin, k…ôn ilat naum…®s, k…ôn ilat koateg…ôs-in suat…®p o n…ôr…ôk…®n…ôn net…ômim. K…ôn n…®kilat t…ôm…ôrioah e nol…ôn rat m…®n …ôh: ilat koatetet net…ômim, ilat iohamnu it…ôm, ilat koatol nat…®mnat it…ôm koatiuw-pa nem…ôha, ilat neiueiu…ô, ilat koatol t…ôrat k…ôm net…ômim. Ilat koat…ôn n…®kal…® net…ômim,  
\v 30 moat…ôn rat net…ômim, ilat koatet…ôhau Uhg…®n, ilat nag…ôt-ir…ôk…®s, ilat nausit moat…ôghat ausit. Ilat koateg…ôs-in suat…®p o nol…ôn t…ôfag…ô rat m…®n it…ôm net…ômim kot…ôruru …ôh. Ilat moat…ôht n…ôwia tata ne mama.  
\v 31 Ilat nen…®k…ô, ilat n…ôghat t…®p…®k, nolkeike…ôn r…ôhalat t…®k…ô o net…ômim, k…ôn nat …ôpnap…®n ilat at…®p m…®n neen, okol t…ôs…ôt…ôl…®g-in…ôn nas…ôk…ôn o nasitu…ôn e net…ômim.  
\v 32 Ilat kot…®tun pap n…ôghat…ôn …ôtuat…®p r…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm tat…ôn m…ôm…ô net…ôm m…®n u koatol nol…ôn m…®n …ôh, kot…ôk…ôike mot…®m…®s. M…ôto ilat koat…ôk…ôike e nol…ôn m…®n …ôh, k…ôn ilat koatol nol…ôn rat tapr…ôk…®s-in nat …ôh, n…®kilat tagien o net…ômim neen m…®n it…ôm koatol nol…ôn rat m…®n …ôh, k…ôn moat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr r…ôhalat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn m…ôm…ô okotol.   
\c 2  
\s1 Uhg…®n otakil mu…ôh m…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôghat…ôn o t…ôfag…ô rat\f + \fr 2:0 \ft E ves m…®n u e 2:1-3:8, Pol tat…ôghat …ôtuat…®p k…ôm net…ôm Isrel. Tat…ôghat-in nol…ôn r…ôhalat it…ôm n…®kilat t…ôht m…ôm…ô kot…ôtuat…®p e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n m…ôto-inu ilat noanol r…ôha Isrel, k…ôn koat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn Lou r…ôha Moses.\f*  
\m
\v 1 Tol n…ôhlan, nat …ôpnap…®n it…ômat net…ômim naka, ok…ôm…ô nakotakil motu…ôh mot…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha suah kit o nol…ôn rat kit r…ôhan,\f + \fr 2:1 \ft Net…ôm Isrel k…ômot…ôn m…ôm…ô Iaihlu…ô m…®n, ilat rafin net…ôm kot…ôrat m…ôto-inu Iaihlu…ô m…®n k…ôm…ôsotos…ôn Lou r…ôha Moses.\f* m…ôto nakotakil motu…ôh mot…ôl…ôh…ôu r…ôhat…ômat at…®p n…ôghat…ôn. K…ôn r…ôhat…ômat n…ôghat…ôn t…®k…ô o nuhalp…®n…ôn, m…ôto-inu it…ômat it…ôm n…ôkoatol n…ôhlan, n…ôkoatol nol…ôn rat m…®n ahmen-ahmen m…®n …ôm elat.\x - \xo 2:1 \xt Mat 7:1-2; Jon 8:7 \x*  
\v 2 K…ôn kitat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô nian Uhg…®n t…ôtakil matu…ôh mat…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôghat…ôn k…ôm net…ômim it…ôm koatol nol…ôn m…®n …ôh it…ôm en…ôm…ôn r…ôk…®s, r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn in t…ôtuat…®p …ôm.  
\v 3 Tol n…ôhlan, nian it…ômat nakotakil motu…ôh mot…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha net…ômim o n…ôrat…ôn r…ôhalat, m…ôto it…ômat n…ôkoatol nol…ôn ahmen-ahmen …ôm, k…ôn okol n…ôsotag…®m…ôn nian Uhg…®n otakil mu…ôh m…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôghat…ôn k…ôm it…ômat.  
\v 4 !N…®kit…ômat t…ôs…ôht p…®k…ôn nol…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n! In tatol t…ôw…®r p…®k k…ôm it…ômat, k…ôn m…ôset…ôhau u…ôhai…ôn it…ômat, k…ôn r…ôhan n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn ot…ômat in t…ôf…ôm…ôh. M…ôto it…ômat n…ôkoatol nat …ôpnap…®n …ôm e nol…ôn w…®r m…®n …ôh r…ôhan. N…ôkot…®tun o k…ôp, m…ôm…ô tatol nol…ôn t…ôw…®r m…®n k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…ôuhlin it…ômat e r…ôhat…ômat nol…ôn rat m…®n.\x - \xo 2:4 \xt Efes 1:7; 2 Pita 3:15 \x*   
\p
\v 5 M…ôto r…ôhat…ômat-kap…ô ti…ôk…®s, k…ôn m…ôsot…ôuhlin…ôn it…ômat e r…ôhat…ômat nol…ôn rat m…®n. K…ôn o nat u, nakotarg…ôtain nem…ôha ne nalp…®n…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n ot…ômat. K…ôn on…ôkotos nem…ôha ne nalp…®n…ôn r…ôhan e nian Uhg…®n otol …ôp r…ôhan n…ôl…ôh…ôu…ôn n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p.  
\v 6 K…ôn Uhg…®n otos-ip…ôn k…ôm net…ômim kiti…ôh kiti…ôh t…ôt…ôu-p…ôn …ôm nat…®mnat it…ôm k…ômotol.\x - \xo 2:6 \xt Sam 62:12; Prov 24:12; Mat 16:27; 2 Kor 5:10 \x*  
\v 7 Uhg…®n otos-ip…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n k…ôm net…ômim it…ôm koat…ôtul …ôskas…®k nian rafin o nol…ôn nat it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p. Net…ôm m…®n …ôh koatalkut p…®k o nol…ôn nat w…®r m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n otos-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat n…ônwiwi…ôn, ne n…®siaii…ôn, ne n…ômeg…ôh…ôn it…ôm namnun t…®k…ô.\x - \xo 2:7 \xt Rom 8:17-18\x*  
