\p K…ôn tol n…ôhlan n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhak tol min-nulan m…ôm…ô, io slef r…ôha Lou r…ôha Uhg…®n e r…ôhak n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn wi, m…ôto e n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn rat r…ôhak, io slef r…ôha lou r…ôha t…ôfag…ô rat.\x - \xo 7:25 \xt 1 Kor 15:57 \x*   
\c 8  
\s1 Nol…ôn r…ôha n…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n  
\m
\v 1 K…ôn n…ôuk…ôt…® n…ôghat…ôn rafin m…®n …ôh tol min-nulan, m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô kitat kot…ôtuat…®p e n…®gan…ômt…®n m…ôto-inu kotahat…ôt…ô e nat it…ôm Kristo t…ômol otat. K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, Uhg…®n kol t…ôsu…ôh…ôn, k…ôn m…ôs…ôl…ôh…ôu…ôn n…ôghat…ôn m…ôsol…ôn nalp…®n…ôn kit r…ôha net…ôm m…®n u k…ômotuwa kiti…ôh ilat Kristo Iesu,  
\v 2 m…ôto-inu n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha Narm…®n, it…ôm tatos-ipa n…ômeg…ôh…ôn wi k…ôm kitat e Kristo Iesu, in t…ôm…®k…®s kitat e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha t…ôfag…ô rat ne n…®m…®s…ôn.  
