\v 4 Uhg…®n t…ômol n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô, n…ôghat…ôn …ôtuat…®p m…®n r…ôha Lou okotuwa motol n…®pahrien…ôn e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhatat it…ôm k…ôsot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn suat…®p r…ôha n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn rat r…ôha et…ômim, m…ôto koat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn suat…®p it…ôm Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôg…ôtun k…ôm kitat.\x - \xo 8:4 \xt Kal 5:16,25 \x*   
