\v 30 K…ôn kitat it…ôm in t…ômaup…ôn m…ôn m…ôm…ô okotuwa r…ôhan, in t…ômaun-in kitat. K…ôn kitat u it…ôm t…ômaun-in, in t…ômol kitat kot…ôtuat…®p e n…®gan…ômt…®n. K…ôn kitat u it…ôm t…ômol kitat kot…ôtuat…®p, in ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr mos-ip…ôn n…®siaii…ôn ne nep…ôt…ôn …ôhag-…ôhag r…ôhan k…ôm kitat.   
\s1 Nolkeike…ôn asol r…ôha Uhg…®n  
\p
