\p
\v 23 M…ôto roiu, r…ôhak w…ôk ik…®n-u t…®nol namnun, k…ôn e nup tep…ôt r…ôk…®s, iakolkeike p…®k m…ôm…ô ek…®mn…ô m…ôplan it…ômat,  
\v 24 k…ôn tol n…ôhlan, n…®kik tat…ôht m…ôm…ô ek…®mn…ô m…ôplan it…ômat nian ekuw…®n …ôp…ôh kantri u Spen. K…ôn nian ek…®mn…ô kotauil…®m o nian …ôku…ôk…®r …ôm, k…ôn iakolkeike m…ôm…ô nakotasitu lak e r…ôhak naliw…ôk…ôn.  
\v 25 M…ôto roiu, iatuw…®n Jerusalem o nasitu…ôn e i…ôfak m…®n …ôh-ik…®n,  
\v 26 m…ôto-inu i…ôfak m…®n …ôp…ôh kantri mil u Masetonia ne Akaea, n…®kilat t…ômagien o nos-ipam…ôn r…ôhalat m…ôni m…ôm…ô ekasitu e ian-rat m…®n e nim…ôfak …ôp…ôh Jerusalem.\x - \xo 15:26 \xt 1 Kor 16:1-4 \x* \x - \xo 15:26 \xt W…ôk 24:17; 1 Kor 16:1; 2 Kor 8:1; 9:2,12 \x*  
\v 27 N…®kilat t…ômagien …ôm o nol…ôn, k…ôn in tahmen e iehl kit it…ôm noanol r…ôha Isrel k…ômotol k…ôm ilat. Tol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu ok…ôm…ô Iaihlu…ô m…®n k…ômotos n…ôw…®r…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n e suat…®p r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, k…ôn Iaihlu…ô m…®n okot…ôk…ôike motasitu e net…ôm Isrel e r…ôhalat m…ôni.\x - \xo 15:27 \xt 1 Kor 9:11 \x*  
\v 28 Oekos m…ôni it…ôm ilat k…ômotos-ipa, muw…®n mos-ip…ôn k…ôm i…ôfak m…®n …ôp…ôh Jerusalem. K…ôn nian emol namnun w…ôk u, k…ôn ekiet Jerusalem muw…®n …ôp…ôh kantri u Spen, k…ôn e r…ôhak naliw…ôk…ôn oek…®mn…ô m…ôplan it…ômat.  
\v 29 Nian ekuwa m…®t…ôlau imat…ômat ik…®n, ek…®tun m…ôm…ô iatos nat…®mnat w…®r tep…ôt e Kristo m…ôm…ô ekos-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat, k…ôn it…ômat on…ôkot…ôto t…ôw…®r lan.\x - \xo 15:29 \xt Rom 1:11 \x*   
\p
\v 30 Piak m…®n ne w…®n…®k m…®n, m…ôto-inu kitat koatahat…ôt…ô e I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôhatat Iesu Kristo, k…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n tatol m…ôm…ô kitat koatolkeike kitat m…®n, ek…ôtap…ôh …ôskas…®k ot…ômat m…ôm…ô n…ôkoat…ôfak ron io k…ôm Uhg…®n, k…ôn e nol…ôn …ôh, nakotasitu lak e n…ôluag…®n…ôn r…ôhak.\x - \xo 15:30 \xt 2 Kor 1:11; Kol 4:3; 2 Tes 3:1 \x*  
\v 31 Ot…ôfak m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n otasitu lak mahtos…®g-in net…ôm Jutia it…ôm k…ôsot…ôn…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô, ok…ôsot…ôr…ôk…®n…ôn io. K…ôn ot…ôfak m…®n m…ôm…ô nian ekuw…®n miet-p…ôn Jerusalem, net…ôm m…®n u koatahat…ôt…ô e Kristo, n…®kilat otagien o r…ôhak w…ôk.  
\v 32 K…ôn e nol…ôn …ôh, ok…ôm…ô Uhg…®n tolkeike mihin, ek…®mn…ô m…ôplan it…ômat e nagien…ôn, k…ôn kitat rafin ag…®n-…ôh, n…®kitat otagien.  
\v 33 P…ôs Uhg…®n it…ôm in n…ôuk…ôt…® n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn t…ôtat…®g it…ômat min. ∆èw…ôh.   
\c 16  
\s1 Pol t…ôtauiat…®pin in m…®n neen  
\m
\v 1 Io iat…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô w…®n…®tat u Fipi, it…ôm tatos w…ôk r…ôha dikon e nim…ôfak …ôp…ôh Kegkria, in p…ôtan w…®r kit.  
\v 2 Iak…ôtap…ôh ot…ômat m…ôm…ô nian in ot…®mn…ô, on…ôkotagien …ôm ron e n…ôrg…® I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôhatat, e nol…ôn it…ôm in t…ôtuat…®p m…ôm…ô net…ômim r…ôha Uhg…®n okotol mihin. Ok…ôm…ô r…ôhan nat kit t…®k…ô, t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô nakotasitu lan, m…ôto-inu in t…ômasitu lak ne net…ômim tep…ôt.   
\li1
\v 3 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Prisila ne Akwila, it…ôm it…®m…ôhal em…ôt…ôhalol w…ôk kiti…ôh r…ôha Kristo Iesu.\x - \xo 16:3 \xt W…ôk 18:2 \x*  
\v 4 Iu…ôhk…®r kiam…®s o nasitu…ôn lak. S…ôn…ôm…ô io p…®s…®n …ôm, m…ôto io ne Iaihlu…ô m…®n rafin u koat…ôfak, it…®mat ekot…ônwiwi Uhg…®n olau.   
\li1
\v 5 K…ôn ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm nim…ôfak it…ôm k…ômotu…ôf…®m…®n e r…ôhalau nim…ô.  
\li1 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm io kit u Epaenetas, u it…ôm t…ômaup…ôn mahat…ôt…ô e Kristo e profens …ôp…ôh Esia.   
\li1
\v 6 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Meri it…ôm t…ômatol p…®k w…ôk ot…ômat.   
\li1
\v 7 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Antronikas ne Junias, natimak mil it…ôm it…®m…ôhal min ilau em…ôhaluw…®n e kalapus. Aposol m…®n koat…®siai-in p…®k ilau, k…ôn ilau k…ômuaup…ôn-in io muahat…ôt…ô e Kristo.   
\li1
\v 8 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Ampliatas, it…ôm iakolkeike e nolkeike…ôn r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.   
\li1
\v 9 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Urpanas, it…ôm kitat koatol w…ôk kiti…ôh e Kristo, k…ôn ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm io kit u Stakis.   
\li1
\v 10 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Apeles it…ôm t…ôm…ôtul …ôskas…®k e Kristo e nian i…ôk…®s m…®n.  
\li1 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Aristopolas ne noanol m…®n r…ôhan, ne r…ôhan iolw…ôk m…®n.   
\li1
\v 11 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Herotian, r…ôhak …ôtuat…®p.  
\li1 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Nasisas ne r…ôhan m…®n, ne r…ôhan iolw…ôk m…®n it…ôm koat…ôfak k…ôm I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.   
\li1
\v 12 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Trifaena ne Trifosa, p…ôtan mil it…ôm k…ôtioal p…®k w…ôk r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.  
\li1 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm io kit u Persis, p…ôtan kit m…®n it…ôm tatol p…®k w…ôk r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.   
\li1
\v 13 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Rufas, i…ôfak w…®r kit r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, ne r…ôhan mama it…ôm t…ômatol t…ôw…®r k…ôm io tahmen e r…ôhak …ôtuat…®p mama.\x - \xo 16:13 \xt Mak 15:21 \x*   
\li1
\v 14 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Asigkritas, ne Filegon, ne Heremes, ne Patropas, ne Heremas, ne piatat m…®n it…ôm ilat min koatat…®g.   
\li1
\v 15 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Filolokas, ne Julia, ne Nereas ne w…®n…®n, ne Olimpas, ne i…ôfak m…®n rafin it…ôm ilat min kotat…®g.   
\li1
\v 16 Ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat m…®n tahmen m…ôm…ô it…ômat kiti…ôh …ôm e Kristo. Nim…ôfak rafin r…ôha Kristo koat…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat.\x - \xo 16:16 \xt 1 Kor 16:20; 1 Pita 5:14 \x*   
\p
\v 17 Piak m…®n ne w…®n…®k m…®n. Iak…ôtap…ôh …ôskas…®k ot…ômat m…ôm…ô nakoat…ôto w…®r it…ômat o net…ôm koatol m…ôm…ô nakot…ôhap it…ômat m…®n, k…ôn koat…ôg…ôtun nat…®mnat it…ôm koatol net…ômim koataki…ô e nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhalat, k…ôn n…ôg…ôtun…ôn …ôh tol p…®s…®n ag…®n e n…ôg…ôtun…ôn it…ôm n…ômotos r…ôk…®s.\x - \xo 16:17 \xt Mat 7:15; Taet 3:10 \x* Ot…ôtul is…ôu olat,  
\v 18 m…ôto-inu net…ôm kotol n…ôhlan, ilat k…ôsotol…ôn w…ôk r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Kristo, m…ôto koatol w…ôk …ôm o nat n…®p…ôt…®lat tolkeike. Ilat koat…ôn w…®r n…ôghat…ôn, k…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhalat t…ôtehen, k…ôn ilat koateiu…ô, k…ôn mat…ôr…ôk…®n n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha net…ômim tep…ôt it…ôm kot…ôruru nat.\x - \xo 16:18 \xt Fil 3:19; 2 Pita 2:3 \x*  
\v 19 Net…ômim k…®not…ôto r…ôk…®s namnus…ôn m…ôm…ô it…ômat n…ôkoatol n…ôwia Kristo. Tol n…ôhlan, n…®kik tagien p…®k ot…ômat. M…ôto iakolkeike p…®k m…ôm…ô nakotenat…®g e nol…ôn …ôtuat…®p m…®n, k…ôn m…ôm…ô n…ôsotuw…®n…ôn e nol…ôn rat m…®n.\x - \xo 16:19 \xt Rom 1:8; 1 Kor 14:20 \x*  
\v 20 Uhg…®n it…ôm n…ôuk…ôt…® n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn, ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn in tegu…ôtain Setan, k…ôn in otat…®g …ôm l…ôhau e nelk…®t…ômat. P…ôs n…ôw…®r…ôn r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu t…ôtat…®g it…ômat min.\x - \xo 16:20 \xt Jen 3:15 \x*   
\p
\v 21 Timoti it…ôm it…®mlau min etioal w…ôk kiti…ôh, tat…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat. K…ôn Lusias, ne Jeson, ne Sosipata u natimak m…®n, k…ôhal…ôn m…®n t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat.\x - \xo 16:21 \xt W…ôk 16:1-2; 19:22; 20:4 \x*   
\p
\v 22 Io Tesias, it…ôm em…ôte n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Pol e naoa u, io iat…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat u kitat kiti…ôh e I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.   
\p
\v 23-24 Kaeas tat…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat. Io Pol, ek…ôtat…®g e r…ôhan nim…ô, k…ôn net…ôm r…ôha nim…ôfak kotu…ôf…®m…®n iman ik…®n.  
\p Erastas u et…ôm tat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e m…ôni r…ôha taon …ôh, ne piatat Kuartas, ilau m…®n katu…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat.\x - \xo 16:23-24 \xt W…ôk 19:22; 1 Kor 1:14 \x*   
\p
\v 25 P…ôs kot…ônwiwi Uhg…®n. In t…®tun nol…ôn m…ôm…ô it…ômat n…ôkoat…ôtul …ôskas…®k e nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhat…ômat. In otol n…ôhlan e namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r r…ôha Iesu Kristo it…ôm iat…ôn-iar…ôp.\x - \xo 16:25 \xt Rom 1:5; Efes 1:9; 3:5,9; Kol 1:26 \x* N…ôghat…ôn u t…ôm…ôhluaig nuw…ôh r…ôk…®s,  
\v 26 m…ôto roiu, t…ômol …ôp in. K…ôn in Uhg…®n u it…ôm tat…ômeg…ôh nian rafin, k…ôn in t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô ekot…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn r…ôha Kristo it…ôm ien m…®n aup…ôn k…ômot…ôte e naoa m…®n r…ôhalat, k…ôn net…ômim okot…®tun. Ekot…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô noanol m…®n rafin e n…ôtueint…ôn, p…ôs ilat okotahat…ôt…ô e Uhg…®n, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan moatol …ôm n…ôwian.  
\v 27 Uhg…®n p…®s…®n …ôm in Uhg…®n, k…ôn in p…®s…®n …ôm in tenat…®g. !P…ôs kot…ônwiwi Uhg…®n nian rafin namnun t…®k…ô, o nat it…ôm Iesu Kristo t…ômol! ∆èw…ôh.   